description: Tortally Tasty is a new food truck hitting the streets of San Diego! They specialize in deliciously unique, hand-crafted tortas. They take this traditionally Mexican sandwich and put their own unique spin on it. With options like The Jon Wayne and Richard Slimmins, you'll quickly discover that these are more adventurous than your average torta. Tortally Tasty also has amazing fries and hand crafted dipping sauces. Check them out, San Diego!
name: Tortally Tasty
